## Table Summary

| Group | Tables | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| **User & Auth** | `users`, `user_role_assignments`, `auth_sessions`, `auth_state_records`, `external_identity_links`, `familysearch_credentials` | User accounts, roles, sessions, OAuth credentials |
| **FamilySearch Data** | `fs_persons`, `fs_person_facts`, `fs_person_names`, `fs_person_sources`, `fs_person_memories`, `fs_parent_child_groups`, `fs_couple_relationships`, `fs_couple_facts` | Cached ancestry data from FamilySearch API |
| **Places & Events** | `canonical_places`, `important_event_definitions` | Geocoded places and historical event definitions |
| **User Tree** | `user_tree_persons` | Links users to their discovered ancestors with generation info |
| **Chat & Conversation** | `chats`, `chat_messages`, `response_bundles` | Chat history and AI response routing |
| **KINARRATIVE Artifacts** | `scene_records`, `story_records`, `epic_records` | AI-generated KINARRATIVE content with playback payloads |
| **Collections** | `saved_artifacts`, `saved_collections`, `collection_entries`, `collection_entry_items` | User-saved and curated KINARRATIVE collections |
| **User Preferences** | `user_profiles`, `user_settings`, `user_consents`, `user_consent_history`, `user_memory`, `user_favorite_people`, `scene_feedback` | Personalization, settings, consent management, feedback |
| **View State & Analytics** | `view_state_snapshots`, `analytics_events`, `admin_audit_logs` | UI state caching, product analytics, admin audit trail |

**Total: 37 tables**
